45
00:02:52,802 --> 00:02:55,304
Tapi tes DNA tak mungkin salah.

46
00:02:57,640 --> 00:03:00,685
Nenekmu yang peragu
melakukannya tiga kali,

47
00:03:04,021 --> 00:03:05,064
