Bujuk dia mengabulkan semua keinginanmu.
Lalu dia akan...

110
00:06:35,733 --> 00:06:36,650
Kau pikir...

111
00:06:38,027 --> 00:06:39,111
aku pengemis?

112
00:06:42,072 --> 00:06:45,659
Aku hanya cemas kau berakhir begitu.

113
00:06:45,784 --> 00:06:50,122
Ini tanda pertama
kejatuhanmu mungkin sudah dekat.

114
00:06:51,790 --> 00:06:53,125
Kenapa ada ini di sini?

115
00:07:17,900 --> 00:07:20,778
<i>Kurasa kau kehilangan penciumanmu
karena cedera itu.</i>

116
00:07:21,362 --> 00:07:23,030
Kau mungkin alami penglihatan ganda,

117
00:07:23,656 --> 00:07:25,032
tapi itu akan menghilang seiring waktu.

118
00:07:25,616 --> 00:07:26,533
Lalu,

119
00:07:27,076 --> 00:07:29,787
apa indra perasa dan penciumanku
akan kembali seiring waktu?

120
00:07:58,065 --> 00:07:59,108
Nona Koki.

121
00:08:00,317 --> 00:08:02,569
Bisa bantu aku?
Kumohon.

122
00:08:07,032 --> 00:08:09,243
Tradisional, dengan roti putih.
Ukuran medium.

123
00:08:10,452 --> 00:08:12,496
Aku sama, tapi ukuran reguler.

124
00:08:19,003 --> 00:08:20,337
Kau dapat panggilan rumah?

125
00:08:28,429 --> 00:08:29,888
Atau terjadi hal buruk?

126
00:08:38,605 --> 00:08:39,565
Kau menangis?

127
00:08:45,195 --> 00:08:46,780
Apa pasienmu meninggal?

128
00:08:52,453 --> 00:08:53,620
Kau juga ingin milikku?

129
00:08:56,123 --> 00:08:58,625
Kata Ji-yong roti lapis ini
membuatnya bahagia.

130
00:08:59,376 --> 00:09:02,463
Mungkin makan ini lebih banyak
akan membuatmu bahagia.

131
00:09:04,089 --> 00:09:05,424
Walau aku tak percaya itu.

132
00:09:08,385 --> 00:09:09,803
Apa aku tampak tak bahagia?

133
00:09:10,304 --> 00:09:11,513
Ya, sedikit.

134
00:09:15,100 --> 00:09:16,101
Tapi tidak.

135
00:09:16,310 --> 00:09:19,229
Benar, siapa yang bisa
lebih bahagia darimu?

136
00:09:19,313 --> 00:09:22,608
Kau dokter.
Kau tampan dan populer di antara wanita.

137
00:09:23,275 --> 00:09:25,402
Benar. Aku diomeli, habis-habisan.

138
00:09:25,986 --> 00:09:27,905
Aku memberitahumu

139
00:09:28,405 --> 00:09:30,949
bahwa perawat itu, Ye-sol, dan aku

140
00:09:31,533 --> 00:09:33,035
tahu kau menyukainya.

141
00:09:34,078 --> 00:09:35,913
- Apa?
- Hari itu, ingat?

142
00:09:36,413 --> 00:09:39,333
Kubilang aku tahu kau menyukainya.

143
00:09:40,584 --> 00:09:44,088
Kau bicara soal perawat itu?
Perawat Bae Na-ra?

144
00:09:44,171 --> 00:09:45,172
Ya.

145
00:09:51,387 --> 00:09:52,554
Maafkan aku

146
00:09:53,972 --> 00:09:55,933
jika berbuat sesuatu
yang menyebabkan kesalahpahaman.

147
00:09:56,141 --> 00:09:57,726
Aku baru sadar

148
00:09:58,560 --> 00:09:59,395
ini kekeliruan

149
00:09:59,478 --> 00:10:00,562
dan kesalahanku.

150
00:10:00,771 --> 00:10:02,940
Aku sahabat Min-seong.

151
00:10:03,065 --> 00:10:06,402
Jadi, bagiku, kau...

152
00:10:41,603 --> 00:10:44,565
Aku mengerti maksudmu.

153
00:10:45,274 --> 00:10:46,817
Bagiku, Dr. Lee...

154
00:10:47,734 --> 00:10:49,319
Kau tetap sahabat Min-seong.

155
00:11:07,337 --> 00:11:08,797
Kerjamu bagus.

156
00:11:08,881 --> 00:11:12,301
Dari sekarang, kecilkan apinya sedikit

157
00:11:12,384 --> 00:11:16,722
lalu masukkan garam dan rumput laut
ke dalam panci dan goreng bersamaan.

158
00:11:16,805 --> 00:11:17,931
Baik.

159
00:11:32,821 --> 00:11:33,822
Susan.

160
00:11:36,575 --> 00:11:37,576
Terima kasih.

161
00:11:38,493 --> 00:11:43,427
<font color="#ffff00">[ KANTIN ]</font>

162
00:11:47,502 --> 00:11:48,587
Baik, cukup.

163
00:11:49,588 --> 00:11:51,548
Saat mulai mendidih, bumbui

164
00:11:51,632 --> 00:11:54,259
dengan garam atau kecap asin.

165
00:11:54,343 --> 00:11:55,552
- Baik.
- Baik.

166
00:11:57,804 --> 00:11:58,639
Bagus.

167
00:12:06,146 --> 00:12:07,522
- Ada apa?
- Apa?

168
00:12:09,691 --> 00:12:11,818
