172
00:12:24,831 --> 00:12:25,791
Benar.

173
00:12:27,876 --> 00:12:28,919
Dia meninggal.

174
00:12:33,006 --> 00:12:34,132
Aku keliru.

175
00:12:58,532 --> 00:13:01,576
Ada apa?
Apa ada sesuatu di wajahku?

176
00:13:16,591 --> 00:13:17,718
