177
00:13:21,221 --> 00:13:23,390
Aroma lezat apa ini?
Apa sup rumput laut?

178
00:13:24,975 --> 00:13:26,101
Ya.

179
00:13:26,727 --> 00:13:28,854
Susan, kau membuat sup rumput laut?

180
00:13:30,564 --> 00:13:32,190
Apa hari ini ulang tahun Michael?

181
00:13:32,899 --> 00:13:34,776
Bukan, aku buat untuk orang lain.

182
00:13:35,777 --> 00:13:37,612
Siapa? Siapa "orang lain" ini?

183
00:13:39,865 --> 00:13:42,242
Maaf meminta ini,

184
00:13:42,868 --> 00:13:45,954
tapi bisakah kau mencicipi
sup rumput laut ini saat matang?

185
00:13:46,455 --> 00:13:47,497
Aku?

186
00:13:48,081 --> 00:13:51,418
Kau yang harus mencicipi.
Kau ahlinya.

187
00:13:54,087 --> 00:13:55,505
Enak.

188
00:14:01,845 --> 00:14:04,681
Kenapa aku merasa melupakan sesuatu?

189
00:14:07,851 --> 00:14:08,852
Ye-sol!

190
00:14:08,875 --> 00:14:10,168
<font color="#ffff00">[ SANATORIUM GEOSUNG ]</font>

191
00:14:10,185 --> 00:14:11,144
Bu Han!

192
00:14:13,666 --> 00:14:15,292
Ada apa?
Kenapa kau menangis?

193
00:14:16,197 --> 00:14:17,740
Kau jahat.

194
00:14:18,352 --> 00:14:20,813
Aku menunggumu karena kau suruh.

195
00:14:21,619 --> 00:14:23,538
Aku terus menunggu,
tapi kau tak kembali.

196
00:14:24,489 --> 00:14:25,782
Kau bicara apa?

197
00:14:26,578 --> 00:14:29,039
